Access_Help
        =       "*"
        =       TokenEscapeChar,Token0
        =       " changes the attributes of all objects matching the"
        =       " wildcarded specification."
        =       13,"Attributes:"
        =       13,"L(ock)",9,9
        =          "Lock object against deletion"
        =       13,"R(ead)",9,9
        =          "Read permission"
        =       13,"W(rite)",9,9
        =          "Write permission"
        =       13,"/R,/W,/RW",9
        =          "Public read and write permission"
        =       13
